Class Entity

java.lang.Object
cz.cvut.fel.pjv.entity.Entity
Direct Known Subclasses:
Boss, Player, Slime, Trader
public class Entity extends Object
class Entity is a parent class of every entity, has the basic variables that are needed (colision, speed,...) and also has getters and settes
